label: Active_gNBs
model_reason: The 'Active_gNBs' parameter in the DU configuration must match the 'gNB_name' in the CU configuration for the DU to successfully connect and start. The error message '_Assert_Exit_' indicates a mismatch, therefore the value is being changed to the correct value from the CU.
reference_reason: Sets Active_gNBs to match gNB_name as string
